      "content": "wait, \"secret added coffee\"? i'm not sure i follow. are you being serious right now? \n\nlook, i don't need jokes, i need professional documentation. if you can't provide a legitimate spec sheet or a real lab report showing the discharge rate under heavy load, i can't justify this to my board. just give it to me straight: is the 24-hour claim strictly theoretical, or is there actual empirical evidence for it? i need a real answer so we can close this out.",
